headline.main: 97-Year-Old Twins Freeze to Death After Falling Outside
headline.print_headline: 97-Year-Old Twins Freeze to Death After Falling Outside

lead_paragraph: Two 97-year-old twin sisters apparently froze to death Saturday after they fell outside and were stranded overnight just steps from one of their Rhode Island homes.
